  <body>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">guofeng-zhaonan-004</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·004.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采蘋.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>于以采蘋？南澗之濱，于以采藻？于彼行潦。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>She gathers the large duckweed,
By the banks of the stream in the southern valley.
She gathers the pondweed,
In those pools left by the floods.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">guofeng-zhaonan-004</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·004.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采蘋.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>于以盛之？維筐及筥，于以湘之？維錡及釜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>She deposits what she gathers,
In her square baskets and round ones.
She boils it,
In her tripods and pans.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">guofeng-zhaonan-004</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·004.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采蘋.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>于以奠之？宗室牖下，誰其尸之？有齊季女。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>She sets forth her preparations,
Under the window in the ancestral chamber.
Who superintends the business?
It is (this) reverent young lady.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
